# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# File     : GRND024-obl-proh-coexist-policy.ttl
# Domain   : Deontic Ontology / ODRL Grounding
# Problem  : Obligation + Prohibition coexist: Duty(a) vs Duty(rfr(a)) distinct
# Refs     : Mohammed et al., What Does ODRL Mean? FOIS 2026
# Generated: 2026-03-26 by gen_foundation_problems.py
# Links    : Discriminating/GRND024-obl-proh-coexist-1.p
#            Discriminating/GRND024-obl-proh-coexist-1.smt2
